name: FingerPunk #001 (Adam)
description: This project pokes fun at the original CryptoPunks. The first one is named Adam, he was the first finger to ever be a punk! He lived in the garden of crypto for many years before being ejected by the server. They say he was banished for trying to add a female FingerPunk to the existing code. Poor guy he was just lonley. :(
